                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="font-weight: bold">Stuff I'd like to see, and is appropriate:</span></span>
<br />
*Bulwark of Alendar to include DOT damage. 
<br />
*longer duration mez.
<br />
*group deagro spell 
<br />
** long duration mez. I'd make this an AA ability with a huge refresh that allows you to multiply next (sucessfull) mez duration by 10. Or make the AA an actual lure based mez with high duration. Still need a big refresh on it, and maybe a peridot reagent (we dont want this to be a standard mez).
<br />

<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="font-weight: bold">Stuff that I think would overpower us or is inappropriate for our class:</span></span>
<br />
*group rune 1500 to group. 
<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">O-v-e-r-p-o-w-e-r-e-d. If this went into the game, it should cost a diamond to cast....at least.</span>
<br />
*revamp of shadow/umbra line for avoidance/mana regen. 
<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Umbra is dead. Just because we once had something, doesnt mean we should always have it.</span>
<br />
*high level self buff (we have shielding, druzzil, umbra, clarity, bulwark... combine these into a self buff to replace either focus or brells.. include a shielding or avoidance mod). 
<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">There should always be a benefit to grouping up with a different class than your own. I think this change would be counterproductive.</span>
<br />
*lower mana cost mez. 
<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">I sort of agree, but I'd rather have longer mez's. I think we need improvement in 'keep lots mezzed' area.</span>
<br />
*single target stun, fast cast high cap (level 70 8-10 secs + something... like mana drain or dispel, low resist). 
<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">This is paladins and clerics area. Overpowered for soloing also.</span> 
<br />
*v3 overhaste. 
<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Bard area</span>
<br />
*v3 imp spell damage buff (pair it with something else useful and a manadot or increased mana cost). 
<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Should be someone else. Not us.</span>
<br />
*pair a nuke with insanity 1300-1500 damage (30-50 lure component) . 
<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Our nuking abilities are pretty good. Especially on efficientcy. Using gather mana I can rival the very top damage positions on some mobs....without charm.</span></span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
